		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="384" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">大雪猪王突然猛冲，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">40%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="426" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">大雪猪王锁定蕈兽，朝蕈兽冲来，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span>伤害，在冲刺终点可造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">216.4%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蕈兽%B7大雪猪王.assets/Image_14.png')" x="596" y="651" blendMode="normal">
