		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="437" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">大雪猪王召唤1个雪猪，雪猪周期性扔出雪球，均造成<span color="#99ffff">20%</span><span>雪猪攻击力的伤害。<br/>击败雪猪可获得</span><span textDecoration="underline">寒冷祝福</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="437" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">大雪猪王锁定蕈兽，在原地猛烈跳动地板，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span>伤害，并在周围产生诸多下落的雪球，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害，有玩家倾向，持续8轮后结束。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
